reviewText: I won't review anything you send me because you wouldnt print the last one I wrote because it told the truth and the staple remover was a piece of junk and you refused to tell the other potential customers what a piece of junk it was. Its a waste of my time to write one of these unless its great.
A must for everyone to see

A must see. Once again Billy Crone has researched and mastered a topic, this time It's all about the topic of AI. After viewing the complete set you will understand there is no need to ponder on "IF" .... Instead you will start to ask the real question ....WHEN?? or How Soon will AI be revealed to the mass populas?
